| `LOG_FILE` | App log file. |
| `MORALIS_LOG_FILE` | Moralis provider log file, default under logs. |
| `INTERACTION_LOG_FILE` | Optional interaction log file. |
| `INTERACTION_LOG_DIR` | Interaction trace directory, default `logs/interactions`. |
| `MORALIS_API_KEY` | Required for live Moralis fetches. |
| `MORALIS_DAILY_CU_BUDGET` | Global daily Moralis CU budget, default about 5,000,000. |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Postgres connection. |
| `REDIS_URL` | Redis connection. |
| `CHART_PROVIDER_ENABLED` | Baseline feature flag for Moralis OHLCV. |
